	<!--Long description of the mod. Single line or multi line. Supports minimal markdown subset-->
	<LongDescription># Change Internal Roads

Replace or upgrade these internal networks inside buildings:
- Roads
- Tram tracks
- Rail tracks

## Notes
- Use the **Internal Roads** toggle to enable this feature.
- Not supported yet: invisible roads.
- Uses the game's native Replace/Upgrade rules; invalid swaps, such as rail track to subway track, remain blocked.
- Buildings with upgrades may conflict with edited internal networks; use with Anarchy if placement is blocked.
	</LongDescription>
